reviews.review:
I'm about 15 hours shy of 300hrs into this game. Going from Rank 20 to 10 is DEFINITELY possible and somewhat enjoyable but if you plan on getting anything higher, I would suggest joining the official discord server to play SWF games. Since the quality of randoms in solos is just GARBAGE. You'll literally want to pull your fucking hair out, and will question out loud to yourself, how people like this even got by in life. Zero map awareness, randoms getting hooked in the first 10 seconds of a match, musical hooks (chairs), DC's on first hook, randoms pulling you off hook in front of killer w/out running Borrowed time etc;

I find that when I play SWF games, I have more fun since we can all coordinate what it is we want to accomplish as a team. And COMS. Why there wasn't some type of In game comm system implemented is beyond me. 

Either way, even at full price this game is worth it. DEF grab it on a steam sale. 8/10.
